| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5456 — Recovery Inhibition (fog)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ad5c97a3-680b-5aa2-a7d4-1d1dc5d3c592"
